      "title": "Identifying Trends in a Bar Graph",
      "problem_text": "<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\">Four different forests were treated successively with 3 different fertilizers. Each fertilizer treatment lasted four months. Fertilizer 1 was used first, followed by Fertilizer 2, then Fertilizer 3. Tree growth was measured in meters after each treatment was completed.</p>\n\n\n  <p style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; color: #1f2937;\">Figure 1</p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px;\"><strong>Graph Description:</strong> Bar graph showing Tree Growth (meters) for each forest across three fertilizer treatments</p>\n  <table style=\"width: auto; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 1.2rem; font-size: 14px;\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: #374151;\">\n        <th style=\"padding: 0.6rem; border: 1px solid #1f2937; text-align: left; color: white; font-weight: 600;\">Forest</th>\n        <th style=\"padding: 0.6rem; border: 1px solid #1f2937; text-align: center; color: white; font-weight: 600;\">Fertilizer 1 (m)</th>\n        <th style=\"padding: 0.6rem; border: 1px solid #1f2937; text-align: center; color: white; font-weight: 600;\">Fertilizer 2 (m)</th>\n        <th style=\"padding: 0.6rem; border: 1px solid #1f2937; text-align: center; color: white; font-weight: 600;\">Fertilizer 3 (m)</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: white;\">\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;\">Forest 1</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; background-color: #fef3c7; font-weight: 600;\">2</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; background-color: #fef3c7; font-weight: 600;\">4</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; background-color: #fef3c7; font-weight: 600;\">6</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: #f9fafb;\">\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;\">Forest 2</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">3</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">5</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">4</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: white;\">\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;\">Forest 3</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">4</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">6</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">8</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: #f9fafb;\">\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;\">Forest 4</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">7</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">5</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">6</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 3rem; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; font-style: italic;\">The graph shows grouped bars for each forest, with three bars representing the three fertilizer treatments.</p>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 2.5rem; font-weight: 600; font-size: 17px; color: #1f2937;\">Based on Figure 1, after each successive fertilizer treatment, the growth in meters of the trees in Forest 1:</p>",
