      "problem_text": "<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\">A scientist conducted multiple trials measuring various properties of a chemical system. The data collected is shown in the table below.</p>\n\n\n  <p style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; color: #1f2937;\">Table 1</p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px;\"><strong>Experimental Data:</strong> Multiple trials with varying conditions</p>\n  <table style=\"width: auto; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 1.2rem; font-size: 14px;\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: #374151;\">\n        <th style=\"padding: 0.6rem; border: 1px solid #1f2937; text-align: center; color: white; font-weight: 600;\">Trial</th>\n        <th style=\"padding: 0.6rem; border: 1px solid #1f2937; text-align: center; color: white; font-weight: 600;\">M (m)</th>\n        <th style=\"padding: 0.6rem; border: 1px solid #1f2937; text-align: center; color: white; font-weight: 600;\">A (m/s²)</th>\n        <th style=\"padding: 0.6rem; border: 1px solid #1f2937; text-align: center; color: white; font-weight: 600;\">X (w/a)</th>\n        <th style=\"padding: 0.6rem; border: 1px solid #1f2937; text-align: center; color: white; font-weight: 600;\">T (°C)</th>\n        <th style=\"padding: 0.6rem; border: 1px solid #1f2937; text-align: center; color: white; font-weight: 600;\">F (N)</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: white;\">\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;\">1</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; background-color: #fef3c7;\">3</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; background-color: #dbeafe;\">4</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; background-color: #fef3c7;\">6</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; background-color: #dbeafe;\">10</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;\">12</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: #f9fafb;\">\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;\">2</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; background-color: #fef3c7;\">5</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; background-color: #dbeafe;\">4</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; background-color: #fef3c7;\">8</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; background-color: #dbeafe;\">10</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;\">12</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: white;\">\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;\">3</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; background-color: #fef3c7;\">7</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; background-color: #dbeafe;\">4</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; background-color: #fef3c7;\">10</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; background-color: #dbeafe;\">10</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;\">12</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: #f9fafb;\">\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;\">4</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">3</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">4</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">5</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">10</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">18</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: white;\">\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;\">5</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">3</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">4</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">6</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">15</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">24</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: #f9fafb;\">\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;\">6</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">3</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">4</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">6</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">20</td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">30</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 3rem; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; font-style: italic;\">Yellow highlighting shows M values; blue highlighting shows constant A and T values in Trials 1-3.</p>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 2.5rem; font-weight: 600; font-size: 17px; color: #1f2937;\">As M increased from 3 m to 7 m, while A and T remained constant, X:</p>",
